    AUTPageConstants class contains constants regarding to the AUT pages.

    Utility Class having methods using BiDi and CDP protocol of Selenium 4.

    BrowserOptionsFactory class is responsible for providing browser options (capabilities) to WebDriver instance for execution in both local or remote.

    Utility Class on Cookies.

    Enums to restrict the browser values supported by the framework.
    Any new browser should be included in this class.
    Category
    Enums to restrict the categories allowed to group test cases.
    Any new category should be included in this class.
    ConfigFactory
    ConfigFactory class is responsible to check validity of data from configuration files, system properties and environment variables and provides those data to other Classes and test methods in this Framework.
    DataSupplierHelper
    DataSupplierHelper class contains Data Suppliers (analogous to Data Providers in TestNG) for test methods.
    DateTimeUtils
    Utility Class for Date and Time Operations using Joda Date Time API.
    Driver
    Driver class is responsible for invoking and closing the browsers.
    Driver class is responsible for setting the driver variable to TLDriverManager.setDriver(WebDriver) which handles the thread safety for the WebDriver instance.
    DriverFactory
    DriverFactory class is responsible for returning WebDriver instance for execution in either local or remote.
    EncodeDecodeUtils
    Utility Class for encryption and decryption of Strings(Passwords), byte[] to Base64 conversion, String to Byte[] conversion etc.
    ExtentLogger
    ExtentLogger is responsible to log different event's status to Extent Report.
    ExtentManager
    ExtentManager class helps to achieve thread safety for the ExtentTest instance.
    ExtentReport
    Perform initialisation and termination of ExtentReports.
    After creating an instance for ExtentTest, it is delegated to ThreadLocal variable for providing thread safety.
    Contains utlity methods for ExtentTest
    ExtentReportHelper
    Helper class for ExtentReport - helps in initial configuration and customization of Extent Reports
    ExtentReportListener
    ExtentReportListener class is a listener class implementing ITestListener
    FakeDataUtils
    Ulility Class having methods to help create unique Alphabetic strings, Numeric strings and AlphaNumeric strings.

    FooterMenuComponent  
    FrameworkAnnotation
    Framework Annotation is user built annotation which is annotated on top of test methods to log the author details and category details to the extent report.
    FrameworkConfig
    FrameworkConfig interface is used by org.aeonbits.owner Library.
    All the keys in the configuration files are mapped in this interface.
    FrameworkConstants
    FrameworkConstants class holds constants used within the Framework.
    FrameworkException
    Custom built BaseException for the framework.
    Extends Runtime Exception and can be thrown anywhere to terminate a program.
